ValidLogo no banner 111Tiny Titanshttps://dappradar.com/dapp/tiny-titans
https://twitter.com/@RealTinyTitans
Not found.https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1653074947219111947/w-fSXdLJ_bigger.jpghttps://twitter.com/@RealTinyTitanshttps://twitter.com/@RealTinyTitans/photohttps://twitter.com/@RealTinyTitans/header_photoTiny Titanshttps://tinytitans.fi/
BATTLE OF THE TITANS
The Tiny Titans are NFTs which you can collect, trade and send forth into battle against each other - all happening decentral within the logic of the deployed smart contract. Each Tiny Titan starts off with level one at mintage but receives a random set of values for its attributes - making each Tiny Titan one hundred percent unique!
MINT YOUR TITAN
Everybody can mint a new Tiny Titan to a wallet - if this wallet does not own a Tiny Titan yet. All you need for minting a new Tiny Titan are 0.25 BNB.
On mint, each Tiny Titan starts off with level one, a random set of values for its attributes and an unique artwork representing it.
BATTLE AND LEVEL
To raise the level of your Tiny Titan you need to battle other Tiny Titans. It doesn’t matter if you win or lose, you will always get experience - you gain much more experience for winning tho. If you want to level your Tiny Titan fast you can increase your winning possibility by either fighting against specific Tiny Titans which attributes you looked up beforehand or by adding powerups to your Tiny Titan which boost its attributes for one battle before attacking others.
TRADE AND COLLECT
Every owner of a Tiny Titan has the possibility to sell his Tiny Titan. For this he sets a price for his collectible, which will add it to our list of Tiny Titans that are up for sale. The owner can still battle others while his Tiny Titan hasn’t been sold. And if he has a change of mind, the owner can always cancel the sell offer.

The Cosmic Landscape of CosmoDoodle
Theoretical physicist Leonard Susskind wrote a whole book dedicated to the so-called cosmic landscape, which is the space of the Super-Megaverse with many ‘pocket universes’, in which habitable zones, such as Earth, can be found.
The diversity of the cosmic landscape suggests very different living conditions. Some planets are too cold, if their orbits are far from the main star of the system. On others, it is too hot, if the distance to the star is minimal. Nevertheless, the point is that any environment can be home to a particular form of life. The inhabitants of the ‘steam room’ planet and the planet-ocean will not be alike – that's for sure. However, each population take the laws of physics on the home planet as familiar and normal as earthlings take the fact that they need air for living, and for comfortable living the temperature at the Earth's surface should be 15 degrees Celsius.
Today there is scientific evidence that the cosmic landscape design includes at least 10^500 habitable zones. This has worked out as inspiration for the galaxy of artists to create unique CosmoDoodle worlds. And you have got a chance to walk along them under the stars...

Not found.https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/1302398882186366976/1682426591/1500x500https://twitter.com/FilFoundationhttps://twitter.com/FilFoundation/photohttps://twitter.com/FilFoundation/header_photoFilecoin Foundationhttps://fil.org/
The Filecoin Foundation (FF) is an independent organization that facilitates governance of the Filecoin network, funds critical development projects, supports the growth of the Filecoin ecosystem, and advocates for Filecoin and the decentralized web. In 2017, the creators of Filecoin envisioned that an independent Filecoin Foundation would serve as the long-term governance body for the Filecoin Ecosystem. They gave the Foundation the mandate to “grow an open ecosystem for decentralized storage” and to “give developers an open and sustainable platform to build, enhance and monetize those services.” They wanted the Foundation to be modeled on Foundations for other open source projects like the Apache Software Foundation, the Mozilla Foundation and the Linux Foundation. The Filecoin Foundation operates independently of Protocol Labs, the organization that designed and built the Filecoin network. As a member of our early-stage team, you will have the opportunity to help define our growth as the organization scales. This is a full-time position, remote from anywhere in the world.

Who we are

How We Work

ValidLogo no banner 111Banksy Swaphttps://dappradar.com/dapp/banksy-swap
https://twitter.com/BanksySwap
Not found.https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1653074947219111947/w-fSXdLJ_bigger.jpghttps://twitter.com/BanksySwaphttps://twitter.com/BanksySwap/photohttps://twitter.com/BanksySwap/header_photoBanksy Swaphttps://banksyswap.com/
Banksy Swap is a new DeFi Yield Farming project on Binance Smart Chain.
Token Info
Name: BANKSY TOKEN
Symbol: BANKSY
Chain: Binance Smart Chain #BSC
Contract: 0x957B82c9FF3E7D7d3B67A2Df9B84A200a7403ab1
 
How it works
Like most of the yield farming on DeFi is done via liquidity pools. A liquidity pool is a smart contract that holds on to and locks the cryptocurrencies/tokens of investors. Liquidity providers contribute to the liquidity of a trading pair pool, such as BANKSY-BNB, by depositing their crypto (in this case BANKSY and BNB) in the pool, receiving LP (Liquidity Pool) BANKSY tokens in return.
The assets in a liquidity pool create a market where the assets can be exchanged by traders. If there were no liquidity pool, it would not be possible for a trader to swap tokens, as there would be no “other side” of the trade. When an investor swaps tokens (e.g. BANKSY for BNB), he needs to pay a trading fee.
This fee is paid to the liquidity providers in proportion to the amount of liquidity (BANKSY and BNB) they have added to the pool. An investor who “owns” a big part of the liquidity pool will receive more trading fees compared to an investor that provided little liquidity to the pool. The fee at Pancakeswap is fixed at 0.17% per token swap trading.
Our team understand the triumph you feel when you find a good farm and the dejection of a rugpull. This farm is a collection of our team's view on what we think are the elements of a successful farm model. For this purpose, we decided on a low emission rate (0.5) to our platform. We believe this model will help end users earn maximum yields over an extended period of time.
Banksy Swap is a novel DeFi Yield Farming project hosted on the Binance Smart Chain. Through liquidity pools that facilitate yield farming, Banksy Swap manages a market for the BANKSY-BNB trading pair. Its distinctive appeal lies in its commitment to maintaining a low emission rate and providing a sustainable farming model that aims to maximize yields over an extended time.

Tezos is a decentralized, public blockchain that evolves by upgrading itself. Stakeholders of the Tezos network vote on amendments to the protocol to reach social consensus on proposals, creating a secure and organic upgrading mechanism. The protocol's on-chain governance system, its consensus algorithm based on Proof-of-Stake (PoS), and its ability to facilitate formal verification of smart contracts, make Tezos an ideal long-term solution for high-value financial applications. Why?
The Financial Crisis of 2008 changed everything. Wealth around the world was decimated. The US government stole money from Main Street to give to Wall Street. Governments have not stopped their reckless spending at the expense of its citizens. Central banks keep printing money, eroding purchasing power. The war on cash has just begun.

ZKX is the first permissionless protocol for derivatives built on StarkNet.  We’re building a decentralized exchange that lets users trade derivatives using reward mechanisms, liquidity provisioning, and simplified access to complex trading strategies. We’re passionate about democratizing access to global yields so anyone can invest in them.
You can read more about our vision, what we’re building, and our roadmap here.
We’re backed by well-known venture funds in the ecosystem. By joining us, you have the opportunity to work with a global team and the chance to shape the future at ZKX.
